  "text": [
    "Oysters adhere",
    "to things, no eyes:",
    "spat on the smooth",
    "curve of a pier",
    "they feel shadows",
    "and snap shut.",
    "The sun wavers",
    "while anchored below",
    "each distills",
    "Tomales Bay,",
    "accreting waves",
    "within its shell.",
    "Voluptuous and cold,",
    "Kumamoto trembles",
    "on a thin fork,",
    "liquefaction",
    "of cloud. Rain",
    "distorts glass,",
    "our tavern submerged",
    "all afternoon."
  ],
  "title": "Hog Island Oysters",
  "year": ""
